item.title: Notre Dame of Maryland University
item.description: Founded more than 100 years ago on the progressive vision that education can transform the world, Notre Dame prepares compassionate leaders who change lives. Notre Dame of Maryland University is an independent, Catholic-affiliated, liberal arts college in Baltimore, Maryland. It contains a Women’s College and coeducational programs for women and men.
